data.description: Popular modified A202 Del Webb home with 1633 square feet of living space. Priced to sell to accommodate for paint, carpet, and ready for your personal touches. This home features two bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an eat-in kitchen designed to be spacious and bright. The kitchen has appliances like a stove, microwave, disposal, and dishwasher, making meal preparation and cleanup convenient. A breakfast nook within the kitchen provides a pleasant spot to enjoy meals while overlooking the large great room, creating an open and welcoming atmosphere. Having inside laundry facilities is a practical feature that adds to the convenience of daily living, while covered parking helps protect vehicles from the elements. A lower HOA (Homeowners Association) fee is certainly appealing, especially since it includes maintenance of green, grassy courtyards, water, sewer & Garbage, and roof replacement.
